\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adef6165db66bbf55734ff4a6b21cc921dcc5efc","tid":800792,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21014a7c89b7d94587907c7c550b8dcea63db390","tid":800792,"uid":49275,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:10:01.000Z","msg":"wiki任人改都可以有人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:14:48.000Z","msg":"喂 又玩選擇性失明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<blockquote>其實好耐之前, 出查冊post嗰時已經知道楊嘉駒先生(Plus 仔) 有另外一間公司, 叫Alpha Tech (HK) Limited 元創(香港)有限公司, 因為當時是想查連登, 而Alpha Tech (HK) Limited 無許業珩身影, 所以無理到。 <br />\n<br />\n查冊post <br />\n<a href=\"http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6684818&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6684818%26page%3D1&d=8o3N58cKbXvOpePAnLU64dr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=5c782f3d\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6684818&amp;page=1</a> <br />\n<br />\n少少背景: Alpha Tech (HK) Limited 嘅股東係 Bash Hammer Limited 除了許業珩以外嘅股東 <br />\nPlus仔 &ndash; 43% <br />\n朱先生（Alxen Chu）&ndash; 30% <br />\n倪先生 &ndash; 23% <br />\n<br />\n好啦, 戲肉嚟啦, 今日屎忽痕去 icris 睇睇Plus仔有咩搞, 先發現原來佢做咗一間叫Grand Surplus HK Limited 嘅公司嘅董事。 <br />\n<br />\n當然要發揮追求真相的精神, 首先發現Grand Surplus係喺今年2月成立, 3月1號 Alpha Tech (HK) Limited 認購咗1000股(不過3月22日先 file), 股東分佈如下： <br />\nAlpha Tech (HK) Limited &ndash; 1000股 <br />\nTop Banana Limited - 2999股 <br />\nMTel Lab Limited - 3000股 <br />\n創始股東 &ndash; 1股 <br />\n<br />\n根據董事變動嘅申報, Plus仔喺3月1號做咗Grand Surplus 嘅董事, 不過3月7號先file, 所以出查冊post嗰時查唔到 (3月2號) ; 可能因為咁, 所以心存僥倖, 喺戰月勇者同連登合作嗰時, 連登扮到好委屈, 完全無利益關係咁 (btw, 仲有其他董事, 一個叫鄺頴軒, 另一個叫黃明威, 應該分別代表Top Banana同MTel, 一陣再講) <br />\n<br />\n咁關戰月勇者乜事 ? <br />\nTop Banana Limited 就係出戰月勇者間公司, 後面係一間創業板上市公司8148奧栢中國集團有限公司, 即係出800萬同達哥合作嗰間 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/GEM/2017/0628/GLN20170628090_C.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkexnews.hk%2Flistedco%2Flistconews%2FGEM%2F2017%2F0628%2FGLN20170628090_C.pdf&d=8o3N58cKbXvOpePAnLU64dr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=e2364bf2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/GEM/2017/0628/GLN20170628090_C.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nGrand Surplus嗰位董事鄺頴軒係奧栢嘅管理層, 年報有講; 加上Grand Surplus 嘅註冊地址其實係奧栢嘅地址, 公司秘書都是奧栢嘅公司, 估計實際上可能是奧栢話事 <br />\n<br />\n奧栢有個董事(副主席)陳偉傑, 根據年報 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/GEM/2017/0324/GLN20170324014_C.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkexnews.hk%2Flistedco%2Flistconews%2FGEM%2F2017%2F0324%2FGLN20170324014_C.pdf&d=8o3N58cKbXvOpePAnLU64dr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=79d7d61c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/GEM/2017/0324/GLN20170324014_C.pdf</a><br />\n陳偉傑先生（「陳先生」）於二零一五年五月七日已獲委任為聯席主席，並在藍鴻震博士於二零一五年十月八日辭任後，於二零一五年十月八日至二零一五年十月十五日成為唯一主席。陳先生於二零一五年十月十六日獲調任為副主席 <br />\n陳先生自二零一六年十二月起獲委任為中國人民政治協商會議第九屆茂名市委員會委員。</blockquote>[/quote]"},{"pid":"82ea6503f0d1418e3467ffaf7fe5711ff0b43249","tid":800792,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:16:36.000Z","msg":"阿派好波"},{"pid":"a2565bfabdc641a66bf0023d62643922c4203ab0","tid":800792,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:18:09.000Z","msg":"回家吧"},{"pid":"b5923c96afc0c004210d063b593001fa7ca780e6","tid":800792,"uid":17606,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"82ea6503f0d1418e3467ffaf7fe5711ff0b43249","tid":800792,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:16:36.000Z","msg":"阿派好波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:19:45.000Z","msg":"連狗人人得而誅之"},{"pid":"8e7f12224626b6f43fd6c769fe0ff280b038904e","tid":800792,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d7c1c46bc4f78b5b0f74b5b744f6d3c55078fff","tid":800792,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de237a70e68169365006fa41e577e8bdc5d985fa","tid":8007